        <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">The RBA cash rate sits at 3.85% as of February 2026. Boat loan rates have a larger spread above the cash rate than car loans due to the factors mentioned above — depreciation risk, environmental exposure, and smaller resale markets.</p>
