        <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f] pr-8 text-left">Can I get a loan for a used boat?</h3><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] flex-shrink-0 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg></summary><div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100"><p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">Yes. Most lenders offer secured boat loans for used vessels, though rates increase with age. Boats under 5-7 years typically qualify for the best rates. Older boats may require an unsecured personal loan or a specialist marine lender. Nik Finance identifies which lenders from our 130+ panel finance your specific vessel.</p></div></details>
